<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="az">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; background: #f9f9f9; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 32px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background: #cf6f94; color: #fff; padding: 28px 32px; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.5rem; }
    .body { padding: 28px 32px; }
    .footer { padding: 16px 32px; background: #fafafa; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #aaa; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header"><h1>📦 Çatdırıldı!</h1></div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Hörmətli {{order.customerName}},</p>
      <p>Sifarişiniz <strong>#{{order.code}}</strong> çatdırıldı. Zövq alın! 🌸</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">Baku Roses · bakuroses.az</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
